1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,000
She said "Hello there" and smiled.

2
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:05,500
"Nice"? That's all you've got?

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,000
It's a 'special' occasion — don't ruin it.

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:10,500
He whispered… "I know what you did."

5
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,000
The price was $50–$100, maybe more.

6
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:15,500
„Guten Morgen", sagte er leise.

7
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,000
❝This is quoted text❞, she replied.

8
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,500
Don't you ❛dare❜ say that again!

9
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:23,000
It was a long—very long—night indeed.

10
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:26,000
"Wait…" he said. ‟Are you sure about this?"
